rows.label: tlk45350351_02_msg0001
rows.name:
You know there's a gate that's always
shut tight here in Port Anangham?

rows.label: tlk45350351_02_msg0002
rows.name:
That gate leads to an area called
Chansagh Wastes. We keep it shut
to ward off the dangerous monsters.

rows.label: tlk45350351_02_msg0003
rows.name:
You could visit the Wastes yourself
if you're looking for a challenge. But if
you're not up to it, I'd steer well clear.
